{
  "text": "Then were there any prophets that we have now recorded that sprung from this era or soon after it? I am Ra. Those of the empire were not successful in maintaining their presence for long after the approximate three zero zero zero 3, 000 date in your history and were, perforce, left with the decision to physically leave the skies. The so-called prophets were often given mixed information, but the worst that the Orion group could do was to cause these prophets to speak of doom, as prophecy in those days was the occupation of those who love their fellow beings and wish only to be of service to them and to the Creator.",
